ygData.messageBody:
Im a human SK (as i assumed you knew, being on this list) and want to
do a bit of travelling.

Anyone know the best way to get to Guk from Qeynos?
And how well or ill are humans treated down there?

Also i would like direction from Qeynos to Befallen.

Keeping in mind of course that Rivervale must be avoided if possible.
I have a Necro comapanion who attempted to make it to Freeport via
Rvervale. Well, her Invis wore off, and she got hacked by the halfling
bastards. She proceeded to die another 6-7 times trying to regain her
corpse.



Thanks
Bathory
Cazic-Thule
